# WSL

* Follow https://github.com/matthewpersico/personal/blob/main/README.md.
* sudo vi sudoers.$USER
   <i><$USER> ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD:ALL<nl>
   %sudo ALL=NOPASSWD: /etc/init.d/cron start<nl>
   <esc:wq>
* sudo chown root:root sudoers.$USER
* sudo chmod 664 sudoers.$USER
* sudo mv sudoers.$USER /etc/sudoers.d/$USER
* Copy shortcuts in C:\Users\matth\Documents\WSL Stuff to shell:startup.
* sudo apt-add-repository ppa:git-core/ppa
* sudo add-apt-repository ppa:kelleyk/emacs
* sudo apt update
* sudo apt upgrade
* sudo apt install...
